│  ● test         - Generating suite for utils.py (8 passed)             │
│  ○ docs         - Idle                                                 │
│                                                                        │
│ Recent Activity:                                                       │
│  [04:02:10] EVENT: File changed (main.py)                              │
│  [04:02:12] ROUTE: Routed change to review agent                       │
